line_1: To nodding crowds his ancient pedigree;
Offspring of God, no less thy pedigree,
line_2: What thou once wert, art now, and still may be,

line_1: Offspring of God, no less thy pedigree,
line_2: Thy God alone can tell, alone decree;

line_1: Yet would you search my pedigree,
line_2: I rose like Venus from the sea:
